A little app using RapLeaf API to retrieve information about your emails contact.
With this app, you could create some events, and it retrieves interested people (supposedly) by itself.
You could email them directly saying you want to invite them to a specific event.

Django/Rapleaf/Google Data Service

Requirement :
- A Rapleaf API key
- Modify the settings.py-dist file to put your own login/password/keys


(Online demo coming soon.)